snippet.title: SeeingRed - LAUNCH TRAILER - [LINK IN DESC]
snippet.description:
The final entry of my video diary series regarding a project scheduled for release this Christmas; Seeing Red Complete Edition


Itch.io Game Download Link: https://true-retrodev.itch.io/seeing-red-complete-edition

GameJolt Game Download Link: https://gamejolt.com/games/Seeing-Red-Complete-Edition/386257


Hyper’s Twitter: https://twitter.com/TheRealHypester

Hyper’s Soundcloud: https://soundcloud.com/hypersonic-fan

The link will be in this description from the 23rd of December 2018. Thank you all for supporting this project, I have been given a place at my dream University so I will always see this project as one of my favourites. I made it for all of you to end this roller-coaster of a year with a bang!

Merry christmas, this is a present from me to you! Expect something big to start off 2019!!
